         <abstract id="aspace_60dd1177b809790625a2b6d9b7cc5ef6">Thirty-one letters written by Argimiro Bosch, a Republican soldier in the Spanish Civil War, to his wife, Angelita Talens Bo, and his family. The letters document Bosch's time as a prisoner in Valencia.</abstract>
