      <bioghist id="aspace_4bbd3ee8a7f5d2ab04d33ce684bc1c3d">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>Argimiro Bosch was Republican soldier in the Spanish Civil War, during which he was held as a prisoner in Valencia.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_cf223db29b0be399612ac87d20d7c497">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Thirty-one letters written by Argimiro Bosch, a Republican soldier in the Spanish Civil War, to his wife, Angelita Talens Bo, and his family. The letters document Bosch's time as a prisoner in Valencia.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
